(483, 1, '2015-11-23 00:23:22', '2015-11-23 00:23:22', '&nbsp;\n\nOnce they graduate from UWC Maastricht, our alumni continue to be part of a growing community of changemakers who aim to improve situations and opportunities for others, increasing the positive impact of a UWC education by reaching out and interacting with others.\n\nIf you are a UWC Maastricht graduate you will surely enjoy joining our alumni platform here <a href=\"https://uwcmaastrichtconnect.com/\">uwcmaastrichtconnect.com</a>\n\nHere are some of the projects our alumni are currently involved in and some of their testimonies:\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li>My name is Taha, UWCM\'15 and I\'m the founder of <a class=\"profileLink\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tedxmisurata/\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=1603167526564360&amp;extragetparams=%7B%22directed_target_id%22%3A176257202553766%7D\">TEDxMisurata</a>.\nTEDxMisurata goes beyond being a normal independently organized TED event, it is an event in which we are trying to make IDEAS the main focus of a group of activists from all around Libya. To use it as a force to unite them and create a community of bright minds in Libya, away from all of the other political issues and the instability.\n<a href=\"http://uwcmaastrichtimpact.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/TEDxMisurata.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-228 aligncenter\" src=\"http://uwcmaastrichtimpact.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/TEDxMisurata-212x300.jpg\" alt=\"TEDxMisurata\" width=\"212\" height=\"300\" /></a></li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;', 'Alumni', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'alumni', '', '', '2015-11-23 00:23:22', '2015-11-23 00:23:22', '', 0, 'http://uwcmaastrichtimpact.com/?page_id=32', 0, 'page', '', 0),
